  "text": "It is worth mentioning that, for embedded applications, even with today's hardware technology for mobile devices, memory space is still a limited, costly resource [CITATION_1] . Thus, when choosing between two classifiers of similar recognition rates, the lesser the number of parameters to be stored, the better is the classifier.",
